content:
Notify Travel Plans as a Self-Service Process (Unmanaged Package)

Capture customer requests for travel notifications through a self-service channel.

Available in: Lightning Experience
Available in: Professional, Enterprise, and Unlimited Editions where Financial Services Cloud is enabled

Configure a self-service portal using the Financial Services Client Portal template to give your customers a self-guided process to provide notice about their travel plans.
title: Notify Travel Plans as a Self-Service Process
